{"tid":755731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人咁怕曬黑","createTime":"2018-07-25T12:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T10:14:36.000Z","uid":62916,"like":19,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1ff8f20f222523b317584274b1d4dc7b8c3079","tid":755731,"uid":62916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:16:20.000Z","msg":"去完旅行番黎，因為成個人曬到甩晒皮同黑左好多，之後比屋企人，女朋友，同朋友係咁話同笑鳩我，話好污糟好核突，成個東南亞人咁。 <br />\n但其實我覺得曬黑個skin tone 做小麥色其實幾靚，好有陽光氣色，不論男同女都係，但留意到身邊好多人包括連登仔女都覺得曬黑好似原罪咁，好似unwire 果個娜姐咁，成日比連登仔話佢好黑點點點。<br />\n<br />\n但其實適當曬太陽都對身體幾好，又可以遮到黑眼圈，吸收陽光和吃含豐富鈣質食物，有助強健骨骼，減低骨質疏鬆及骨折風險。<br />\n<br />\n睇下以下報道：<br />\n<em>惟不少港人，特別是年輕女性愛白皙皮膚，謝絕戶外活動及曬太陽，堪稱「見光死」，以致維他命D不足，影響鈣質攝取，增加日後患骨質疏鬆的風險。醫生指出，港人缺乏戶外運動，鈣質吸收量僅為建議水平的三至四成，與內地、印度、巴基斯坦幾近「睇齊」。每日做戶外運動半小時或以上、飲兩杯牛奶，有助強化骨骼；長者可定期驗骨質密度，及早預防骨折。<br />\n<br />\n香港骨質疏鬆學會會長何堯炘指出，預料本港二○一五年的髖骨折手術個案將較○九年增加七成。現時每年有四千五百宗髖骨折個案，但未獲當局列為優先處理病症。市民到公立醫院測試骨質密度，平均要輪候兩至三年。他表示，港人每周平均只花一小時做戶外活動，吸收陽光不足，令身體製造維他命D不足，阻礙吸收鈣質，「好多年輕女性怕曬太陽，搽好厚防曬，令身體少咗維他命D，影響攝取鈣質；過度瘦身，亦會令骨質流失。」他建議市民做適量負重運動，如行山或步行，有助強壯骨骼。<br />\n</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201533_12e053e83383673b110349e56a75d9e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201533_12e053e83383673b110349e56a75d9e8.png&h=7a97c378&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201535_4ec1d58b623a4916508a909cfdc48c8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201535_4ec1d58b623a4916508a909cfdc48c8d.png&h=b7e1e8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201537_babb61315a55bf9c03bc8d26b499e6c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201537_babb61315a55bf9c03bc8d26b499e6c7.png&h=c5d44d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201537_855ca1b619901c6bb4bd9603ae0bdd3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201537_855ca1b619901c6bb4bd9603ae0bdd3d.png&h=1263e7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201538_855ca1b619901c6bb4bd9603ae0bdd3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201538_855ca1b619901c6bb4bd9603ae0bdd3d.png&h=caee820e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/201540_5428f7bc40cd8b6381cb2e17272eea86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F201540_5428f7bc40cd8b6381cb2e17272eea86.png&h=44823368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解香港人咁怕曬黑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5ddfe2d83bdab18d40df7bd9083a564f2a1143","tid":755731,"uid":78533,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"即係你黑得唔靚囉"},{"pid":"645455593a02ee7618e0fd2f436e92ba5857be2c","tid":755731,"uid":62916,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9b5ddfe2d83bdab18d40df7bd9083a564f2a1143","tid":755731,"uid":78533,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"即係你黑得唔靚囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"黑小小就比條女同老母話 做咩又曬黑，好核突咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f035d6fba631c84873b15af0a871ed110d2ad26","tid":755731,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"我黑得黎係灰，唔係小麥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43883e34bbbfb899afa4726ba4640fef92b4b616","tid":755731,"uid":34023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"黃皮白心